        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.1 概述"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                102,
                194,
                122
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "H3C LA2608-GM/GU 室内无线网关（以下简称 LA2608）可以为用户提供无线服务，为了实现对设备的管理，LA2608需要通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                138,
                905,
                174
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/0e2eb77b873265be02b023ce2afe6cf44de34b831f737f62b241d4317d028886.jpg"
                },
                "content": "",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                146,
                188,
                184,
                212
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                188,
                198,
                223,
                212
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "目前，LA2608只支持与 H3C公司的无线控制器互通。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                224,
                561,
                239
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2 配置LA2608与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                282,
                482,
                302
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如 图 1 所示，LA2608 安装了SIM卡，通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器，并向用户提供无线服务。关于LA2608的安装方法，请参见“H3C LA2608室内无线网关 快速安装指南”。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                320,
                905,
                355
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/f204a8881b1075be8d2d10c4dc2e261e7f3bcf139057a7bd2350d558b8ea6198.jpg"
                },
                "content": "```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    A[\"Host A\"] -->|WIFI| B[\"LA2608\"]\n    C[\"Host B\"] -->|WIFI| B\n    D[\"Host C\"] -->|WIFI| B\n    B -->|3G/4G| E[\"Internet\"]\n    E --> F[\"AC\"]\n```",
                "image_caption": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "图1 配置 LA2608与无线控制器互通"
                    }
                ],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "sub_type": "flowchart",
            "bbox": [
                147,
                391,
                808,
                584
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2.1 配置LA2608"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                625,
                260,
                642
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(1) 配置拨号访问组的拨号控制列表"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                659,
                438,
                675
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "<LA2608>system-view "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                684,
                310,
                695
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]dialer-rule 1 ip permit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                700,
                413,
                712
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(2) 配置 DCC 拨号"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                716,
                305,
                732
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/e381047ffd55b50c2649968ebbf1e1fb8204f864fcbd8adbaa7c23aafd4126f5.jpg"
                },
                "content": "",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                747,
                186,
                770
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "说明"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                188,
                756,
                225,
                771
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "dialer number命令用来配置发起呼叫的拨号串，不同运营商的拨号串不同，请用户在配置前向网络运营商获取发起呼叫的拨号串。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                141,
                781,
                904,
                815
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]interface Cellular-Ethernet2/0\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]ip address cellular-allocated\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer enable-circular\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer-group 1\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer idle 0 "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "powershell"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                850,
                645,
                929
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "page_number",
            "content": {
                "page_number_content": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                505,
                948,
                514,
                958
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer autodial 5\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer number *99# autodial\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]nat outbound\n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]quit "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                51,
                626,
                114
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(3) 配置 DNS 解析功能"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                117,
                342,
                133
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]dns resolve "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                141,
                310,
                153
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(4) 配置静态路由"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                157,
                295,
                173
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608]ip route-static 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 Cellular-Ethernet2/0 "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                181,
                660,
                194
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "(5) 指定运营商无线控制器的 IP 地址"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                142,
                197,
                445,
                213
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "[LA2608] wlan ac ip 60.191.99.143 "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "txt"
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                220,
                430,
                233
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1.2.2 配置运营商无线控制器"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                90,
                248,
                352,
                264
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/8595b5e0431211ff1fcc244ac1d195c418463eea29d726b873ccc03e27578124.jpg"
                },
                "content": "",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
